										<item>
											<widget class="QCheckBox" name="cbMetroidUseFirmwareLanguage">
												<property name="text">
													<string>Use DS Firmware Language (EU-style Auto Patch)</string>
												</property>
											</widget>
										</item>
										<item>
											<widget class="QLabel" name="lblMetroidUseFirmwareLanguageDesc">
												<property name="text">
													<string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;body&gt;
Reads your DS firmware language and patches the game to display in that language.&lt;br&gt;
The EU ROM has a hidden Japanese option — setting your DS firmware to Japanese activates it.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;EU / US ROM:&lt;/b&gt; Works in all modes (multiplayer and adventure).&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;JP ROM:&lt;/b&gt; Works in multiplayer only. &lt;font color=&quot;red&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Adventure mode will not be playable with this enabled.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;KR ROM:&lt;/b&gt; Not yet supported.
&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
												</property>
												<property name="wordWrap">
													<bool>true</bool>
												</property>
											</widget>
										</item>
									</layout>
								</widget>
							</item>

